&lt;p data-start=&quot;1071&quot; data-end=&quot;1347&quot;&gt;The ideal candidate is someone who enjoys understanding how a business operates financially, improving processes, and building scalable systems. Over time, this person will expand into broader finance responsibilities, including reporting, FP&amp;amp;A support, and process ownership.&lt;/p&gt;
