&lt;p data-start=&quot;1913&quot; data-end=&quot;1968&quot; data-is-last-node=&quot;&quot; data-is-only-node=&quot;&quot;&gt;Join us in building the power foundation of the future!&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Role Summary&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;335551550&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335551620&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559738&amp;quot;:240,&amp;quot;335559739&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;We are&amp;nbsp;seeking&amp;nbsp;a technically sharp and strategically minded Staff Patent Engineer to join our team, focused on protecting and advancing our intellectual property portfolio in medium voltage solid-state transformer (SST) technology. In this role, you will serve as a senior IP leader at the intersection of&amp;nbsp;cutting-edge&amp;nbsp;power electronics engineering and patent strategy, driving innovation identification, portfolio development, and IP governance in close collaboration with R&amp;amp;D leaders, product teams, and legal counsel.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:false,&amp;quot

